snippet.title: Pixel Galaxy Trailer
snippet.description:
Grow. Make friends. Survive together.

Enemies become friends in this hectic-paced, Katamari-inspired shoot ‘em up.

Coming 2015 to Steam on PC and Mac. Coming to consoles early 2016.

pixelgalaxygame.com
